We detect you have a Jahrwoxi on board. We ask you to leave.
My apologies. We were just passing through, and we were about to stop at the Keck Sigma Moon, but it's been destroyed. What happened?

We saw a strange ship attack there. It destroyed the moon and took all of its weapons then headed through the Cygnus LeapGate. Now we suggest that you and your pet Jahrwoxi go on your way!
